
OrangeHRM Command (v 1.0)

This command allows you to manage your OrangeHRM AWS instance completely from the terminal.

Usage:
    orangehrm install                   Start the OrangeHRM web application installation
    orangehrm upgrade                   Upgrade an existing instance of the OrangeHRM application
    orangehrm status                    Display the installed status of the OrangeHRM web application
    orangehrm version                   Display the version of the OrangeHRM command
    orangehrm create-login-message      Create a login message script that will display the install status on SSH
    orangehrm backup                    Backup an existing instance of the OrangeHRM web application
    orangehrm restore                   Restore a backup of the OrangeHRM web application
    orangehrm help                      Display this message   

To remove the orangehrm command, delete /home/ec2-user/.orangehrm

